snippet.title: EP3. Greg Ellis is The Respondent w/ Bettina Arndt: Amber Heard's #MeToo Playbook Exposed + DVRO's
snippet.description:
Order of Australia recipient Bettina Arndt joins Greg Ellis to discuss the #MeToo playbook and Amber Heard's silver bullet ruination strategy of Johnny Depp. 

Professor Janice Fiamengo joins for the post episode Q&A to discuss how toxic feminism is destroying so much of our society and culture.
